longBusinessSummary: FenixOro Gold Corp. engages in the acquisition and exploration of gold projects in Colombia and the United States. The company also explores for silver and copper ores. Its flagship property is the Abriaqui project covering approximately 547 hectares located in Antioquia State, Colombia. The company was formerly known as American Battery Metals Corp. and changed its name to FenixOro Gold Corp. in May 2020. FenixOro Gold Corp. was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
